       <strong>
        Cutting-Edge 3D Metal Architectures
       </strong>
       <br/>
       Prof. Jennifer Lewis' lab at Harvard has unveiled the ability to pattern planar and freestanding nanoscale-sized 3D metallic architectures. [
       <a href="http://wyss.harvard.edu/viewpressrelease/257">
        more
       </a>
