 <p>
 </p>
 <strong>
  LMI Featured in DOE Article
 </strong>
 <br/>
 A recent featured article from the DOE Office of Science mentions the work performed by Drs. Atwater and Yablonovitch on advancing the efficiency of silicon solar cells. [
 <a href="http://science.energy.gov/news/featured-articles/2016/03-17-16/">
