 </a>
 <p>
  <strong>
   Light Management in LSCs
  </strong>
  <br/>
  A  collaboration between the Nuzzo and Alivisatos groups has demonstrated
          enhanced photon collection in luminescent solar concentrators. [
  <a href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1021/acsphotonics.5b00630">
   more
  </a>
  ]
  <span class="date">
   02.05.16
  </span>
